								<li>2nd place: 3000 RP, 10-Win IP Boost </li>
								<li>3rd place: 1800 RP, 10-Win IP Boost </li>
								<li>4th place: 1000 RP, 10-Win IP Boost</li>
								<li>5th-8th place: 10-Win IP Boost</li>
							</ul>

