							<ul>
								<li>1st place team: 1000 points per player</li>
								<li>2nd place team: 800 points per player</li>
								<li>3rd place team: 600 points per player</li>
								<li>4th place team: 500 points per player</li>
								<li>5th place team: 400 points per player</li>
								<li>6th place team: 300 points per player</li>
								<li>7th place team: 200 points per player</li>
								<li>8th place team: 100 points per player</li>
							</ul>
					</div>
					<div class="col-md-6">
						<h4>End of Series</h4>
						<p>Individual with most series points</p>
						<ul>
								<li>1st place player: $250</li>
								<li>2nd place player: $150</li>
								<li>3rd place player: $100</li>
								<li>4th place player: $75</li>
